1
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:40,130
[Born to Be Alive]

2
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:43,200
[Episode 39]

3
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:44,900
Do you know Zhou Fusheng?

4
00:01:47,780 --> 00:01:48,560
Who?

5
00:01:48,910 --> 00:01:50,620
The account holder
who transferred you the money

6
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:51,880
is named Zhou Fusheng.

7
00:01:51,930 --> 00:01:53,200
He's a migrant worker from the south.

8
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,300
He admitted he needed money

9
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:56,030
and sold his ID to someone else.

10
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:56,990
Why do you think

11
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:59,060
this guy named Chen

12
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,310
used a false identity

13
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,370
to get close to you?

14
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,290
I don't know.

15
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,230
I...

16
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:05,910
I really don't know.

17
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,520
Mr. Meng!

18
00:02:12,060 --> 00:02:12,620
Mr. Meng.

19
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:13,800
Mr. Feng is on the phone for you.

20
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,130
Are you there, Mr. Meng?

21
00:02:17,250 --> 00:02:17,970
Mr. Meng!

22
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:23,050
Coming.

23
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:27,240
We couldn't get anything else

24
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,170
out of Wang Jian.

25
00:02:28,690 --> 00:02:29,240
The lead ended

26
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,770
at the remittance account.

27
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:32,760
Although there's no evidence

28
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:33,480
proving

29
00:02:33,650 --> 00:02:34,310
Meng Yaohui

30
00:02:34,329 --> 00:02:36,220
is the one who moved Wang Jian
to another location.

31
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,340
He suddenly appeared

32
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:39,340
at the scene where I found Wang Jian.

33
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:41,460
That makes him highly suspicious.

34
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:43,710
If it really is Meng Yaohui,

35
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:46,010
he may attempt to flee.

36
00:02:46,740 --> 00:02:47,960
I'll apply

37
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,440
for an exit ban on him.

38
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:52,420
The DNA has been sent

39
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:53,640
for expedited testing.

40
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,400
The results should be back soon.

41
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:55,900
Okay.

42
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:01,330
What's wrong?

43
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:03,360
Tell me.

44
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,270
The DNA results

45
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,680
aren't out yet.

46
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,340
It's all just theory at this point.

47
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:11,630
Every theory

48
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,110
could bring us one step closer

49
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:14,050
to the truth.

50
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,840
Go ahead.

51
00:03:18,930 --> 00:03:20,579
Wang Fumin and Meng Yaohui

52
00:03:21,130 --> 00:03:22,180
left Tianduo at the same time

53
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:23,640
when Duojie went missing.

54
00:03:24,470 --> 00:03:25,300
Wang Fumin might have

55
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,240
fled abroad,

56
00:03:26,260 --> 00:03:27,520
whereabouts unknown.

57
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,730
Meng Yaohui lied

58
00:03:28,730 --> 00:03:30,160
about going to Guangzhou.

59
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,510
But the evidence suggests

60
00:03:31,510 --> 00:03:32,970
he might have gone abroad.

61
00:03:34,130 --> 00:03:34,960
These two

62
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:36,720
are likely the ones who killed

63
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:37,380
and hid

64
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:38,780
Duojie's body.

65
00:03:40,540 --> 00:03:41,800
It's even possible...

66
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:15,240
Come in.

67
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,000
What's going on

68
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,260
with Wang Fumin's son?

69
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:35,980
Why are the police looking for him?

70
00:04:44,370 --> 00:04:45,500
You're not talking?

71
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,190
Fine.

72
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,570
Go.

73
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:21,270
That body...

74
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,490
is indeed Wang Fumin's.

75
00:05:31,990 --> 00:05:33,390
What about Duojie's?

76
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:42,990
I'm asking you about Duojie.

77
00:05:43,180 --> 00:05:44,890
Did you kill him or not?

78
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:47,220
Yes.

79
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,500
Where is the body?

80
00:05:49,590 --> 00:05:51,190
I threw it into Cangduo Lake.

81
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:52,670
The fish would've

82
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:53,630
taken care of it.

83
00:05:53,650 --> 00:05:55,780
It's impossible for anyone to find it.

84
00:05:58,050 --> 00:05:59,659
That was the safest

85
00:05:59,780 --> 00:06:00,880
and most efficient way

86
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,470
I could think of at the time.

87
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:13,570
Then what about

88
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:15,160
Wang Fumin's body?

89
00:06:16,130 --> 00:06:17,790
Didn't you say he went abroad?

90
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,120
Wang Fumin...

91
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,180
I killed him, too.

92
00:07:11,470 --> 00:07:12,170
Wang.

93
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:13,310
Where is he?

94
00:07:13,810 --> 00:07:14,480
Almost there.

95
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,680
Two kilometers left.

96
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,070
A sand-colored Jeep.

97
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:18,460
Got it.

98
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,860
What happened?

99
00:09:52,290 --> 00:09:53,790
How could you be so careless?

100
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:54,600
Who knows?

101
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:56,450
He was like

102
00:09:56,660 --> 00:09:57,870
a wild yak.

103
00:10:19,350 --> 00:10:20,040
This time,

104
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,390
we split it thirty-seventy.

105
00:10:23,310 --> 00:10:24,760
What did you do this time?

106
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,780
Getting thirty percent
is already too much.

107
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,770
Seventy for me, thirty for you.

108
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,240
Just because of this,

109
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:38,010
I deserve more.

110
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:41,020
Otherwise, you cover

111
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,360
my medical bills.

112
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:45,130
I fired the gun.

113
00:10:45,170 --> 00:10:46,720
I threw the body in the lake.

114
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,850
If it weren't for the boss,

115
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,900
you'd get ten percent at most.

116
00:10:53,250 --> 00:10:54,120
Meng.

117
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:57,880
Don't risk your life

118
00:10:59,130 --> 00:11:00,990
for money you won't live to spend.

119
00:11:18,290 --> 00:11:19,380
In a rush,

120
00:11:20,860 --> 00:11:21,620
I had to drive the car

121
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:22,640
out into the wild

122
00:11:23,090 --> 00:11:24,900
and bury his body.

123
00:11:27,810 --> 00:11:29,660
Just for fifty thousand yuan,

124
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:34,010
you killed Wang Fumin?

125
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:38,010
I was young and impulsive.

126
00:11:39,370 --> 00:11:40,410
I lost my head.

127
00:11:43,450 --> 00:11:44,290
So, you knew all along

128
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:45,550
that the body was Wang Fumin.

129
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:47,550
Why didn't you say it from the start?

130
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:52,440
I didn't expect

131
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,860
that after so many years,

132
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:55,520
the body could still be found.

133
00:11:57,860 --> 00:11:58,520
I panicked.

134
00:11:59,890 --> 00:12:00,980
You panicked?

135
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:06,080
You kept a gun

136
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:07,630
for 17 years

137
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:11,230
and managed to stash it
in Wu Jiang's trunk?

138
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,290
Why do I feel like

139
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:17,290
you planned this all along?

140
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,500
No.

141
00:12:19,830 --> 00:12:20,700
I just didn't expect

142
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:22,560
that a moment of impulse back then

143
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:25,220
would

144
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:27,680
spiral out of control.

145
00:12:37,630 --> 00:12:38,270
Enough.

146
00:12:40,710 --> 00:12:42,110
We're done with you here.

147
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,150
Go.

148
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:41,340
You heard all that, right?

149
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,090
This guy can't be trusted.

150
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:50,410
Even a Tibetan Mastiff bites its master.

151
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:53,060
A Tibetan Mastiff

152
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:54,190
only has one master.

153
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,960
You're keeping a wolf

154
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:56,690
by your side.

155
00:13:58,020 --> 00:14:00,420
Figure out how you're
gonna deal with this.

156
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:01,330
Since you're here,

157
00:15:02,220 --> 00:15:04,000
why not come up and sit for a while?

158
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,800
You can chat with my mom for a bit.

159
00:15:05,980 --> 00:15:06,410
The person upstairs

160
00:15:06,410 --> 00:15:07,250
talking to her

161
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:08,400
should've been you.

162
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:11,240
Don't work so late from now on.

163
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,820
Aren't you working overtime, too?

164
00:15:16,820 --> 00:15:17,860
My work

165
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:19,840
will be over soon.

166
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:56,850
Mr. Meng is back.

167
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:02,750
Thank you for your hard work.

168
00:16:11,120 --> 00:16:11,790
Mom.

169
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:15,280
Are you coming back tonight?

170
00:16:15,890 --> 00:16:18,150
Should I leave the door unlocked for you?

171
00:16:18,290 --> 00:16:19,480
I'm not coming back tonight.

172
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:20,370
No need.

173
00:16:22,050 --> 00:16:23,250
Get some rest.

174
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:24,890
Okay.

175
00:16:24,970 --> 00:16:26,080
You go to bed early, too.

176
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:26,610
Bye-bye.

177
00:16:39,820 --> 00:16:40,490
Hello?

178
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:48,930
You're back.

179
00:16:52,900 --> 00:16:53,940
I told you,

180
00:16:54,410 --> 00:16:55,700
imported liquor hits hard.

181
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:56,580
Drink less.

182
00:17:06,220 --> 00:17:08,280
There's twenty million yuan inside.

183
00:17:08,579 --> 00:17:11,380
The password is the anniversary
of my dad's death.

184
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:22,960
What's wrong?

185
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,030
Not enough for you?

186
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:28,400
Or are you upset

187
00:17:28,700 --> 00:17:30,630
the password isn't your birthday?

188
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:34,950
I don't want this money.

189
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:40,030
You're really drunk?

190
00:17:46,310 --> 00:17:47,880
Bai is downstairs.

191
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,180
When you came back just now,

192
00:17:50,180 --> 00:17:51,360
didn't you see her?

193
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,360
I'm not smart enough,

194
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:00,910
but I understand everything.

195
00:18:02,820 --> 00:18:03,770
I know

196
00:18:04,610 --> 00:18:05,370
why someone

197
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:06,930
is watching me downstairs.

198
00:18:08,060 --> 00:18:09,030
I also know

199
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:11,540
why you

200
00:18:11,570 --> 00:18:13,030
want to give me this money.

201
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,480
I also know

202
00:18:16,410 --> 00:18:17,410
that back then,

203
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:20,880
you never went to Guangzhou.

204
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:24,900
Don't worry.

205
00:18:25,790 --> 00:18:27,310
I didn't tell Bai.

206
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:34,010
After I remarried,

207
00:18:35,850 --> 00:18:37,510
I went to Guangzhou to find you

208
00:18:37,810 --> 00:18:39,270
at the address you gave me.

209
00:18:42,290 --> 00:18:43,820
Then why didn't you tell me?

210
00:18:53,390 --> 00:18:55,000
When I received your gifts,

211
00:18:55,330 --> 00:18:56,440
I was very happy.

212
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,420
I kept telling myself,

213
00:19:00,740 --> 00:19:02,400
if my son still cares about me,

214
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:03,420
that's all I need.

215
00:19:04,810 --> 00:19:05,570
I thought

216
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:08,630
I could fool myself

217
00:19:08,630 --> 00:19:10,030
like this for a lifetime.

218
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:14,050
But it doesn't work.

219
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:16,590
In the end,

220
00:19:18,050 --> 00:19:18,500
I didn't even have

221
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,760
a single person who would speak honestly

222
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:20,700
to me.

223
00:19:35,870 --> 00:19:37,600
Do you want me to turn myself in?

224
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,600
Or are you going to turn me in?

225
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:45,220
In this life,

226
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:48,920
the two people I owe the most

227
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:50,970
are you

228
00:19:51,570 --> 00:19:52,680
and your father.

229
00:19:55,290 --> 00:19:56,400
Yaohui.

230
00:19:58,180 --> 00:20:00,830
Don't turn into someone like me.

231
00:20:49,600 --> 00:20:50,680
I told you,

232
00:20:51,570 --> 00:20:52,900
I don't want that money.

233
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:54,420
Pack your things.

234
00:20:55,110 --> 00:20:56,570
We're leaving the country

235
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:57,520
in two days.

236
00:21:22,810 --> 00:21:23,550
You're back.

237
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:28,000
I have a business trip tomorrow.

238
00:21:29,330 --> 00:21:30,730
So I can't drink too much.

239
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:32,640
Just a little.

240
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,720
Is this

241
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:38,960
the last meal?

242
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:42,150
A make-up drink.

243
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:46,560
What do you have to apologize for?

244
00:21:47,420 --> 00:21:48,290
I don't think

245
00:21:48,570 --> 00:21:50,230
I did anything wrong, either.

246
00:21:57,780 --> 00:21:59,080
You still think

247
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:01,740
we are the ones who were wrong.

248
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:03,480
I don't know.

249
00:22:05,570 --> 00:22:06,440
I only know

250
00:22:06,530 --> 00:22:07,330
that there are

251
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:09,000
things I can do

252
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:11,170
and people who need me.

253
00:22:13,310 --> 00:22:15,090
If I turn my back on Xinhai,

254
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,110
I'm turning my back

255
00:22:17,110 --> 00:22:18,840
on the last ten years of who I am.

256
00:22:20,830 --> 00:22:21,690
I can't do that.

257
00:22:26,090 --> 00:22:27,150
You're a smart man.

258
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:31,910
But I have one condition.

259
00:22:35,370 --> 00:22:37,370
I hope you can let Bai Ji off the hook.

260
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:42,860
You know why Xinhai

261
00:22:42,860 --> 00:22:44,260
is giving him a hard time.

262
00:22:54,980 --> 00:22:56,180
I remember that year

263
00:22:57,610 --> 00:22:59,540
when I was still deputy mine chief,

264
00:22:59,770 --> 00:23:01,430
the barrier on the upper bench

265
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,680
suddenly collapsed.

266
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:04,790
I took the hit for you.

267
00:23:05,630 --> 00:23:06,590
You broke a bone.

268
00:23:07,940 --> 00:23:09,270
I've always remembered

269
00:23:09,530 --> 00:23:10,580
that favor.

270
00:23:12,740 --> 00:23:14,430
Being too honest

271
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:16,580
can get you into trouble.

272
00:23:17,180 --> 00:23:18,960
Not everyone appreciates it.

273
00:23:19,810 --> 00:23:20,830
I saved you,

274
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:22,400
and yet I'm the bad guy?

275
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:28,730
Good to see you back.

276
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:46,500
Who is it?

277
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:47,700
Lin,

278
00:24:48,590 --> 00:24:49,310
it's me.

279
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:50,880
Zhang Qinqin.

280
00:24:52,740 --> 00:24:53,600
Sit down.

281
00:24:54,150 --> 00:24:55,410
I'll pour you some tea.

282
00:24:57,210 --> 00:24:59,410
I brought you some moxibustion sticks.

283
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:00,920
Zhu Li mentioned a long time ago

284
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,570
that she wanted you
to learn how to use it.

285
00:25:02,570 --> 00:25:03,510
I've been busy.

286
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,210
It just came to mind now.

287
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:08,340
She...

288
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:09,920
She went on a trip

289
00:25:10,630 --> 00:25:11,370
to Hangzhou

290
00:25:12,460 --> 00:25:13,860
over these past few days.

291
00:25:14,250 --> 00:25:14,810
Well,

292
00:25:15,250 --> 00:25:16,300
I'll take this time

293
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:17,500
to learn it properly.

294
00:25:17,510 --> 00:25:18,910
You really should learn.

295
00:25:19,070 --> 00:25:20,280
When you retire

296
00:25:20,670 --> 00:25:22,130
and go to Jianshe's place,

297
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:24,140
she'll be counting on you.

298
00:25:28,810 --> 00:25:30,460
Time really flies.

299
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,350
Back in Mazhi,

300
00:25:32,980 --> 00:25:34,640
when Zhu Li had heart trouble,

301
00:25:35,110 --> 00:25:37,440
I advised her to move
to a lower altitude place.

302
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,290
She said

303
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:41,010
she couldn't bear to leave those children,

304
00:25:41,010 --> 00:25:42,400
and she couldn't leave you

305
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,340
alone in Mazhi.

306
00:25:44,740 --> 00:25:46,140
Getting old makes me nostalgic.

307
00:25:46,140 --> 00:25:47,140
I can't help

308
00:25:47,810 --> 00:25:49,210
rambling about the past.

309
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:51,440
In other words,

310
00:25:52,790 --> 00:25:53,900
in the end,

311
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,160
what we remember most clearly

312
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,640
always seems to be things

313
00:25:56,670 --> 00:25:57,600
from our youth.

314
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,000
Maybe...

315
00:26:04,250 --> 00:26:04,920
That was the best time

316
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:05,950
of our lives.

317
00:26:08,310 --> 00:26:09,570
Back then, we had drive

318
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:10,910
and ambition.

319
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:14,940
A few days ago,

320
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:16,390
Bai Ju went back to Mazhi.

321
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:25,750
Who is it?

322
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,010
Wen.

323
00:26:27,590 --> 00:26:28,330
Manager Bai.

324
00:26:28,850 --> 00:26:29,240
Sit.

325
00:26:30,690 --> 00:26:31,210
Sit.

326
00:26:33,050 --> 00:26:34,070
Can you pull up the surveillance footage

327
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:34,980
from July 23rd

328
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:35,770
to July 26th

329
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:37,290
at the company entrance?

330
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:38,510
Sure.

331
00:26:38,980 --> 00:26:40,240
Did something happen?

332
00:26:40,310 --> 00:26:40,940
It's a private matter.

333
00:26:40,940 --> 00:26:42,000
Don't tell anyone.

334
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:43,070
I lost something.

335
00:26:43,330 --> 00:26:43,870
Okay.

336
00:26:52,530 --> 00:26:53,660
Is it easy to look up?

337
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:54,840
Yes. Just a moment.

338
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:23,780
Wen.

339
00:27:25,250 --> 00:27:26,140
This... this license plate.

340
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:26,950
Zoom in a bit.

341
00:27:27,780 --> 00:27:28,240
Okay.

342
00:27:36,770 --> 00:27:38,370
I haven't been back in years.

343
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:39,770
Mazhi County

344
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,170
must have changed a lot.

345
00:27:42,430 --> 00:27:44,430
Bai Ju said there are traffic lights

346
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,950
and running water now.

347
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:47,270
I heard

348
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:48,590
that soon,

349
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:51,090
across the Mazhi River,

350
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:53,030
they're developing a new district.

351
00:27:53,030 --> 00:27:53,790
That's good.

352
00:27:54,380 --> 00:27:54,960
Good.

353
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:56,880
She also said
that she met an old herdsman

354
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,740
at the animal husbandry station.

355
00:27:59,230 --> 00:28:00,230
He mentioned you.

356
00:28:01,030 --> 00:28:02,440
He mentioned that snowstorm

357
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:03,540
in the '90s—

358
00:28:04,420 --> 00:28:05,790
more than half

359
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,360
of their livestock died.

360
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,070
It was County Mayor Lin

361
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:11,640
who helped them secure

362
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:12,920
livestock and fodder.

363
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,570
He also took the risk

364
00:28:14,830 --> 00:28:16,340
to apply to the superiors

365
00:28:16,370 --> 00:28:18,180
to waive the animal husbandry tax.

366
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:19,910
The livestock in Mazhi today

367
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:21,290
are mostly

368
00:28:21,570 --> 00:28:22,250
the offspring

369
00:28:22,250 --> 00:28:23,380
of the livestock he secured

370
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:24,440
back then.

371
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:26,810
Without County Mayor Lin,

372
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,970
there would be no Mazhi today.

373
00:28:34,080 --> 00:28:35,880
I really want to see

374
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:39,080
what Mazhi looks like now.

375
00:28:50,810 --> 00:28:52,030
Last night,

376
00:28:53,010 --> 00:28:54,410
Zhu Li called me.

377
00:30:12,140 --> 00:30:12,700
What...

378
00:30:14,130 --> 00:30:15,060
What did she say?

379
00:30:17,030 --> 00:30:18,070
She said

380
00:30:18,130 --> 00:30:20,590
only after living to this age
did she realize

381
00:30:21,590 --> 00:30:22,760
that sometimes, having too much

382
00:30:22,760 --> 00:30:23,820
isn't a good thing.

383
00:30:25,900 --> 00:30:26,720
Money,

384
00:30:27,070 --> 00:30:27,810
status,

385
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:29,110
power—

386
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:30,810
all of it.

387
00:30:32,430 --> 00:30:33,880
But there is one thing

388
00:30:34,460 --> 00:30:36,120
that's better when it's full.

389
00:30:37,250 --> 00:30:38,090
What is it?

390
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:41,570
The moon.

391
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:45,420
She said she really misses

392
00:30:45,590 --> 00:30:47,430
the full moon in Mazhi.

393
00:30:49,700 --> 00:30:50,900
She said she used to think
the moon

394
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:51,720
looks the same

395
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:52,960
wherever you are,

396
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:55,010
and there's no difference.

397
00:30:56,530 --> 00:30:57,770
But now she feels

398
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:00,440
the moon in Beijing

399
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:03,440
is different

400
00:31:04,270 --> 00:31:05,270
from the one here.

401
00:31:07,070 --> 00:31:08,180
Maybe

402
00:31:08,270 --> 00:31:09,670
the higher the altitude,

403
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:12,540
the closer you are to the sky,

404
00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:14,820
the more beautiful it looks.

405
00:31:33,990 --> 00:31:34,640
Did...

406
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:45,120
Did she tell you all that?

407
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:49,460
She said she regretted it,

408
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,340
but it was too late.

409
00:32:03,780 --> 00:32:05,580
Excuse me, is Lin Peisheng home?

410
00:32:12,700 --> 00:32:13,900
Is Lin Peisheng home?

411
00:32:46,190 --> 00:32:47,010
Ma'am.

412
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:48,920
Ma'am, hey, you.

413
00:32:51,390 --> 00:32:52,240
Come here.

414
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:54,720
Clean up

415
00:32:54,740 --> 00:32:56,470
the General Manager's office.

416
00:32:58,960 --> 00:32:59,510
Okay.

417
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:01,930
Take out the trash in the office

418
00:33:01,930 --> 00:33:03,130
and the inner office.

419
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:04,240
Be quick about it.

420
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:12,930
Alright, alright.

421
00:33:12,930 --> 00:33:13,730
Mop the floor,

422
00:33:13,750 --> 00:33:14,700
and do the inner room, too.

423
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:15,430
Hurry up.

424
00:33:24,430 --> 00:33:25,630
Hello? What's wrong?

425
00:33:27,110 --> 00:33:28,070
What's the rush?

426
00:33:28,100 --> 00:33:29,360
I'll go find it for you.

427
00:35:03,690 --> 00:35:05,720
Excuse me, is Lin Peisheng home?

428
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:11,520
Yes.

429
00:35:34,330 --> 00:35:35,990
Are you Comrade Lin Peisheng?

430
00:35:37,550 --> 00:35:38,170
I am.

431
00:35:39,340 --> 00:35:40,840
We are from the Provincial
Discipline Inspection Commission.

432
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,070
Please come with us.

433
00:35:45,860 --> 00:35:46,990
Let me grab a jacket.

434
00:35:59,900 --> 00:36:00,830
Director Zhang,

435
00:36:02,830 --> 00:36:04,060
I can't blame anyone

436
00:36:04,090 --> 00:36:05,420
for how I ended up today.

437
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,290
Ultimately,

438
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,460
I only have myself to blame

439
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:11,650
for making the wrong choice
at a critical moment.

440
00:36:11,650 --> 00:36:12,500
I don't have the face

441
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:13,840
to go back to Mazhi

442
00:36:14,210 --> 00:36:14,980
to face

443
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:17,000
my former leaders and the herdsmen.

444
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:19,760
If you ever go back to Mazhi,

445
00:36:25,530 --> 00:36:26,530
please tell them,

446
00:36:27,310 --> 00:36:29,570
"County Mayor Lin owes them an apology."

447
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:53,380
Hello.

448
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:54,550
The DNA test results

449
00:36:54,550 --> 00:36:55,300
are out.

450
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:56,750
What is the result?

451
00:36:56,750 --> 00:36:57,900
According to the results,

452
00:36:57,900 --> 00:36:59,500
the tested individual is conclusively

453
00:36:59,500 --> 00:37:01,050
the biological parent of the deceased.

454
00:37:01,050 --> 00:37:02,510
The victim is Wang Fumin.

455
00:37:03,050 --> 00:37:03,730
Meng Yaohui

456
00:37:03,750 --> 00:37:04,950
is the prime suspect.

457
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:06,980
Okay, I see.

458
00:37:07,610 --> 00:37:08,560
You guys come in first.

459
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:09,730
Notify the bureau immediately

460
00:37:09,730 --> 00:37:10,590
to send backup.

461
00:37:10,730 --> 00:37:11,530
What's wrong?

462
00:37:11,680 --> 00:37:13,160
I found a Type 56

463
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:13,940
semi‑automatic rifle

464
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:15,210
in Meng Yaohui's office.

465
00:37:15,210 --> 00:37:15,800
A rifle?

466
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:17,400
Get out of there now.

467
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,330
We'll be there as soon as possible.

468
00:37:26,250 --> 00:37:27,780
What's wrong, Manager Bai?

469
00:37:28,170 --> 00:37:28,670
Mr. Meng is back.

470
00:37:28,670 --> 00:37:29,800
I need to talk to him.

471
00:37:29,990 --> 00:37:30,440
Do...

472
00:37:30,540 --> 00:37:30,980
do you want me

473
00:37:30,980 --> 00:37:31,740
to copy the surveillance footage for you?

474
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:32,390
No need!

475
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:49,070
Mr. Meng,

476
00:37:49,090 --> 00:37:50,070
you're back.

477
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:50,520
Um,

478
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:51,590
she's almost done cleaning.

479
00:37:51,590 --> 00:37:52,090
Who asked you

480
00:37:52,090 --> 00:37:53,150
to clean my office?

481
00:37:53,650 --> 00:37:55,150
I thought you were away on business,

482
00:37:55,150 --> 00:37:55,880
so I had someone come

483
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,610
to give it a thorough cleaning.

484
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,010
Ma'am,

485
00:38:00,130 --> 00:38:00,720
Mr. Meng is back.

486
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:01,460
Come out.

487
00:38:05,570 --> 00:38:06,170
It's fine.

488
00:38:06,900 --> 00:38:07,800
You can go do your work.

489
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:08,110
Okay.

490
00:38:08,110 --> 00:38:09,710
Call me if you need anything.

491
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,130
Take this away,  too.

492
00:38:31,330 --> 00:38:33,110
[Mine No. 2 Cash Ledger
of Xinhai Coal Mine]

493
00:38:38,630 --> 00:38:40,490
Are you going back empty-handed?

494
00:38:46,710 --> 00:38:47,600
You're late.

495
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:49,640
The stuff in the secure records room

496
00:38:49,640 --> 00:38:50,970
has already been moved.

497
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:56,810
I've been with Feng Keqing
for over ten years.

498
00:38:57,090 --> 00:38:58,300
I know him too well.

499
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:05,360
Go right now

500
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:07,420
and wipe the accounts

501
00:39:07,770 --> 00:39:09,230
in the confidential room.

502
00:39:09,590 --> 00:39:10,610
And Bai Chun

503
00:39:11,340 --> 00:39:13,000
has been with me for ten years.

504
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:15,180
I know exactly

505
00:39:16,490 --> 00:39:17,890
what he's thinking, too.

506
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:27,460
You're a smart person.

507
00:39:28,530 --> 00:39:29,820
And you know exactly

508
00:39:30,900 --> 00:39:31,960
what I'm thinking.

509
00:39:33,890 --> 00:39:34,920
I was never going

510
00:39:34,950 --> 00:39:36,750
to work for Feng Keqing forever.

511
00:39:39,050 --> 00:39:39,510
These are

512
00:39:39,510 --> 00:39:41,710
the surveillance records and accounts

513
00:39:41,720 --> 00:39:42,980
from Xinhai Coal Mine.

514
00:39:43,490 --> 00:39:45,220
He doesn't know I kept a backup.

515
00:39:46,690 --> 00:39:47,710
These are enough to prove

516
00:39:47,710 --> 00:39:49,910
the illegal mining at Xinhai Coal Mine.

517
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:09,010
I have only one request.

518
00:40:15,260 --> 00:40:16,280
Please

519
00:40:18,470 --> 00:40:19,610
give me two days.

520
00:40:22,050 --> 00:40:23,510
You want to be a good person

521
00:40:23,990 --> 00:40:25,070
report Xinhai

522
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,210
and then just walk away?

523
00:40:31,610 --> 00:40:32,380
I beg you.

524
00:40:34,110 --> 00:40:35,440
Please give me a chance.

525
00:40:40,910 --> 00:40:41,980
I originally planned

526
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:44,540
to send these things
to Reporter Shao in two days.

527
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:45,600
Since you're here,

528
00:40:46,370 --> 00:40:48,030
giving them to you is the same.

529
00:40:49,090 --> 00:40:50,090
With these,

530
00:40:50,730 --> 00:40:51,210
you won't have to

531
00:40:51,210 --> 00:40:52,260
dig any further.

532
00:41:18,530 --> 00:41:19,360
You're right.

533
00:41:21,070 --> 00:41:21,550
I didn't expect

534
00:41:21,550 --> 00:41:23,000
my work to end

535
00:41:25,200 --> 00:41:26,800
even faster than I imagined.

536
00:41:29,050 --> 00:41:30,090
I will treat these

537
00:41:30,450 --> 00:41:31,520
as if I got them

538
00:41:31,550 --> 00:41:33,150
from the confidential room.

539
00:41:38,670 --> 00:41:39,270
Thank you.

540
00:41:41,470 --> 00:41:42,650
That's a huge favor you're doing

541
00:41:42,650 --> 00:41:43,220
for me.

542
00:41:45,090 --> 00:41:46,790
And thank you on behalf of my mom.

543
00:41:46,790 --> 00:41:47,810
Don't say that.

544
00:41:49,570 --> 00:41:50,610
I'm not even sure

545
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:52,470
if I can give you two days.

546
00:41:55,420 --> 00:41:55,870
Okay.

547
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:01,510
See you.

548
00:42:04,450 --> 00:42:06,310
Maybe I shouldn't say, "See you."

549
00:42:16,010 --> 00:42:16,550
See you.

550
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:35,410
Bai.

551
00:42:39,430 --> 00:42:40,960
You left something behind.

552
00:42:53,910 --> 00:42:54,990
That's not mine.

553
00:42:57,510 --> 00:42:58,050
It is.

554
00:43:00,900 --> 00:43:02,190
Because you knew

555
00:43:02,970 --> 00:43:04,220
that kind of oil

556
00:43:05,520 --> 00:43:07,030
wouldn't be used on hinges.
